# V5.59 cold-chunk 异步救援:暴露 ServerChunkManager.addTicket / removeTicket(ChunkTicketType, ChunkPos, int)
# 用于 PlayerSpawner.tryDetectColdChunk 绕过 setChunkForced(true) 的同步 chunk 加载等待。
# vanilla setChunkForced 内部走 chunk.addTicket + getChunk(FULL,true),后者在 cold chunk 上
# park 主线程 1+s(watchdog 抓到 1168ms)。直接调 addTicket 只注册 FORCED ticket,vanilla
# chunk worker thread 异步加载,主线程零 park。
# 配对释放:VPM.releaseForcedSpawnChunks 走 removeTicket 而非 setChunkForced(false) — 后者
# 依赖 ServerWorld.forcedChunks set 已记账,我们跳过了 vanilla set 注册,要走对称 API 路径释放。
accessible method net/minecraft/server/world/ServerChunkManager addTicket (Lnet/minecraft/server/world/ChunkTicketType;Lnet/minecraft/util/math/ChunkPos;I)V
accessible method net/minecraft/server/world/ServerChunkManager removeTicket (Lnet/minecraft/server/world/ChunkTicketType;Lnet/minecraft/util/math/ChunkPos;I)V

